50|$|Singeing {{machines}} can be {{of three}} types: <b>plate</b> <b>singeing,</b> roller singeing, or gas singeing. Gas singeing is widely used in the textile industry. In gas singeing, a flame comes into direct contact to the fabric and burn the protruding fiber. Here, flame height and fabric speed is the main concern to minimize the fabric damage.|$|E

